18870.「プレシアンナの新しいダンスかあ。\n いやあ 楽しみだな。:
Prescianna's new dance, huh? Well, I'm looking
forward to it.

18875.「あは<heart> みんな いい子ちゃんね。\n あなたたちは 幸運よ。:
A-ha<heart> You guys are good kids. You are
lucky.

18876.「……だって このプレシアンナの\n 最高のダンスを 見られるんですもの。:
...because we get to see this Prescianna at
her best dance.

18877.「今日のショーは 一生 忘れられなくなるわよ<heart>: You will never forget today's show <heart>.

18879.「これが 人間の限界を超えたダンスよ！: This is dancing beyond human limits!

18880.プレシアンナは 人間とは思えない\nまるで 獣のような動きで 踊りだした。:
Prescianna began to dance with movements that
were almost too beastly to be human.

18881.一心不乱に踊っているプレシアンナは\n徐々に 魔物の姿へ変わっていった。:
Prescianna, dancing with all her heart,
gradually changed into the form of a monster.

18882.それを観ていた客たちは 徐々に\nしかばねへと 変わっていった……。:
The audience watching the show gradually
turned into measles...

18883.「あは<heart> みんな よかったでしょ？\n あたしのダンス<heart>: Ha-ha-ha. Wasn't it great, everyone? My dance!

18884.「……なっ そんなバカな。\n あたしのダンスが 効かないですって……。:
That's absurd. You said my dance doesn't
work...

18885.「その 金色に輝くオーラ……。\n まさか あなたも モンスターゾーンに……。\:
That golden aura... you don't think you're in
the Shocking Twist too... but it's different
from mine. Why?

18887.「あたしの目に くるいは なかった。\n あなたは あたしをドキドキさせてくれる:
There was no rift in my eyes. You make me so
excited. I haven't felt like this in a long
time.

18888.「あなたと あたし。\n どちらが神に近い スーパースターか……。:
You and me. Which one of us is closer to God,
the superstar...

18890.「あは<heart> 何回やっても 結果は同じよ。\n でも あなたと戦うのは楽:
No matter how many times I do it, the result will be the same. But I enjoy fighting you, so I'll do it as many times as I
can.

18893.「あたしは 天才なのよ……？\n なぜ あなたに勝てないの……？: I'm a genius. Why can't I beat you?

18894.「……プレシアンナ。\n 自分のチカラに おぼれたようね。:
Prescianna. You seem to have drowned in your
own power.

18895.「モンスターゾーンは 自分以外の能力を\n 吸収することで 到達するものじゃない:
Shocking Twist isn't something you reach by
absorbing abilities outside of yourself.

18896.「ただ ひたすら 自分と見つめ合い\n 精進し 弱さを克服した者が\n 怒りによ:
It's an area of expression triggered by the anger of those who have overcome their weaknesses by looking at themselves and
devoting themselves to it.

18897.「あなたは あせりすぎたようね……。: You were in too much of a hurry...

18898.「……あは<heart> サルバリータ。\n あたしとの才能の差に絶望して 自滅:
Sarubarita. That's quite a thing to say from
an auntie who self-destructed in despair over
the difference in talent between you and me.

18900.「<cs_pchero>……。ステキだったわよ。\n あなたとのバトル……。\n:
<cs_pchero>... it was beautiful. Your
battle... it was like dancing in a blissful
dance.

18901.「あんなに楽しいダンス……。\n あは<heart> 生まれて はじめてだったか:
It was the first time in my life that I had
such fun dancing... haha <heart>.

18903.「……プレシアンナ。\n 化け物みたいな 才能の持ち主だったわ。: ...Prescianna. She was a monster of a talent.

18904.「地道な努力を かさねていたら\n きっと 誰の手にも届かないような高みに\n:
I am sure that if you had made steady efforts,
you would have reached heights that would have
been beyond anyone's reach...

18906.「見事だったわよ。<cs_pchero>。\n すっごいプレゼントを あげるから:
That was brilliant. <cs_pchero>. I have a
great present for you, so come to the tavern
in Megistris later.
